:2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:17:44.000Z","msg":"應該集中返去攻差館入面啲私家車<br />\n起碼告暴動佢架車都冇得賠<br />\n跳閘ok, 燒黨鐵觀感唔好<br />\n拆機都可以免, 我觀察左幾日就算部機散撚晒啲人都係會俾錢"},{"pid":"3ba9ad1d6480292ea232cc25dc924e8df974860c","tid":1556110,"uid":67813,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"有咩難睇？有冇傷到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨鐵夾埋差佬圍補示威者仲難睇"},{"pid":"aeb7498be0cade304aace56854830d9f99d052d4","tid":1556110,"uid":2403,"like":2,"dislike":61,"score":-59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:19:40.000Z","msg":"佢老幾呀 再嘈 d前線去燒埋佢屋企添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849f72329e5a98099ab7e5e50eee6e3e71de0f99","tid":1556110,"uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"五毛好似執到寶咁"},{"pid":"3bdd461f948cc0fada7bc06edde15aecf88686e9","tid":1556110,"uid":41317,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"3ba9ad1d6480292ea232cc25dc924e8df974860c","tid":1556110,"uid":67813,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"有咩難睇？有冇傷到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨鐵夾埋差佬圍補示威者仲難睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"真係難睇架屌<br />\n我身邊啲呀姐好多都屌燒黨鐵<br />\n應該要遮廣告牌, 等廣告商覺得喺黨鐵落廣告冇用<br />\n咁先做到可觀嘅經濟損失"},{"pid":"56dd5e61fe62ebed5ed0c35bba241d3e6706df3d","tid":1556110,"uid":255333,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:22:47.000Z","msg":"光明頂啱啱至話可能係臥底放火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a493bad204ae3e7741564524579efb985bc4daa","tid":1556110,"uid":149306,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"所有呢啲都係狗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e645d04b1ec22c067e150d870c0c58646184cc","tid":1556110,"uid":128995,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"有批評就要接受, 講得岩既咪理解下, 唔岩咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都係向住同一目標就得"},{"pid":"1a346cb2321654b357d0f1602c79368dc39c00f1","tid":1556110,"uid":53666,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"党？ 觉？"},{"pid":"5b41b6d9e0ea20f70fe7e6a6fc66320b47127b2e","tid":1556110,"uid":31491,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ba9ad1d6480292ea232cc25dc924e8df974860c","tid":1556110,"uid":67813,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"有咩難睇？有冇傷到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨鐵夾埋差佬圍補示威者仲難睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"宜家又唔係會考<br />\n難唔難睇唔係拉curve去計既<br />\n毅進仔考0分 唔係高過佢就叫考得好"},{"pid":"6bb3167c39613df2a871e8be570007cc3fc80ab7","tid":1556110,"uid":47905,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:29:01.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n無可能有任何行動係全部人都接受<br />\n始終有人激進 有人無咁激進<br />\n<br />\n但諗清楚<br />\n呢幾日個月<br />\n我地既手足受左幾多傷<br />\n燒黨鐵既原因係咩,我諗大家都清楚<br />\n如果你覺得係文宣唔夠,好多人唔明白,咁你唔係應該怪手足<br />\n而係去做文宣,同身邊既人解釋點解咁做<br />\n<br />\n對比手足受過既傷,燒黨鐵只係微不足道的一件事<br />\n<br />\n希望吳先生等人諗清楚<br />\n如果你覺得香港仲有法律仲有方法,可以制裁度班恐怖份子,你地可以做<br />\n如果你都諗唔到可以做到D咩黎保護前線,保護其他和平既市民<br />\n咁你地就唔該交比前線既手足去保護<br />\n落力D解釋返比其他人知點解要咁做"},{"pid":"6eac75e69b99eb854ef3b853993f120773bc7202","tid":1556110,"uid":29625,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"咪講咗成個下晝<br />\n唔係做法問題，係文宣不足問題<br />\n有時間無限loop不如幫手做下文宣啦"},{"pid":"f2cbc7555d23f266cd2947cbb50fe64be82b0f10","tid":1556110,"uid":79987,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:29:16.000Z","msg":"香港人權監察記者人命錄取真相 點解冇人理！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555901</a>"},{"pid":"0dd6ea09e880674d94ceadb390d3d07cdcba37b9","tid":1556110,"uid":2